    "transliteration": "ALLAAHUMMA WAFFIQNEE FEEHE LE-MOWAAFA-QATIL ABRAARE WA JANNIB-NEE FEEHE MORAAFAQATAL ASH-RAARE WA AAWENEE FEEHE BE-RAHMATEKA ELAA DAARIL QARAARE BE-ELAAHIYYATEKA YAA ELAAHAL A'ALAMEENA.", 
    "english": "The O Allah, on this day, (please) lead me so that I will correspond with the upright ones, keep me away on this day from the company of the evils, and lodge me on this day, on account of Your mercy, to the Abode of Perpetual Settlement, in the name of Your godhead, O God of the worlds!"
